n| ✅ | V2-IO-10 | **门禁与回归**：Client 禁 engineIOModule；host/memory/validation 测绿；隔离 005/020 仍为 0 | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio |\n| ⬜ | V2-IO-11 | **文档收口**：18/19/20、engine-boundaries、AGENTS、README 用法与 23 交叉链接一致 | true |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":169,"fileSize":8515,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_执行索引.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":150},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-bedd9673-4483-4c89-977d-07d014696afc-3\nfc_3d464a9a-e5c5-945f-8dfb-f8d10daca8cb_2","startedAtMs":"1784786253904","completedAtMs":"1784786254090"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-1-x7ch","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786254046}
