e` / `beginCall` / 对话 → `endCall`。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":37,"content":"4. 需要持久化经历态时由门面触发 Profile / Memory 相关保存（经 Port）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":40,"content":"注入 Port","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"  → loadWorkspace（ContentPort）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"  → ensureProfile(userId)（ProfilePort）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"       → 经 Port 写 Profile / Memory（若本通需要）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"## 你需要实现或注入什么","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"| 读故事包 / 角色 / 卡 | Content / Workspace Port |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"| 读写信 Profile | Profile Port |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"| 记忆投影与 commit | Memory Port |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"| 引擎旁路日志 | EngineLog Port（可选，视宿主） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"- **不要**在浏览器里直接 `createEngineHost` 并塞本地文件 Port。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"- 浏览器只发 XHR 到你的后端；由 **server/壳** 持有 Host + IO。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":68,"content":"- 若将来「引擎跑在浏览器」：注入的 Port 应是 **XHR 客户端适配**，不是 `fs`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":76,"content":"- 样例包：`data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/` 等（由 ContentPort 读取）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":24,"totalMatchedLines":24,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-85ed9986-aad6-4594-ba66-8cadf12aafa5-13\nfc_b6ea22e2-e5b1-9180-84e6-24754a42b527_5","startedAtMs":"1784786269640","completedAtMs":"1784786269799"},"mod