{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-969cfc14-4ffe-4f6c-a35c-a2469c0c9887-17\nfc_b5d6edd3-d965-94f8-86ea-b159bf8924eb_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md","limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 20. 记忆存储与投影（SQLite）\n\n相关：[12](../需求/12-记忆模型.md) · [13](../需求/13-工具与能力注册.md) · [05](./05-技术选型与工程边界.md) · [18](./18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) · [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)\n\n> **结论：** Content = JSON 文件；**Memory = SQLite**（经 `MemoryPort`）。  \n> **实现落点：** Sqlite 适配在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（迁出后）；引擎只认 `MemoryPort` 契约，不内置 better-sqlite3。  \n> 存得下 ≠ 查得起、注得起。表结构与预算可随实现微调；本文为 v1 初稿。\n\n## 1. 职责切分\n\n| 数据 | 存储 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 故事包 / 角色 Def / 卡 / 资产 meta | JSON 文件 | 作者向、可 diff |\n| Profile 薄存档（Board、story 变量、research、schedule…） | JSON `profile.save.json` | **不含**万级 episodic 数组 |\n| NPC 记忆条目 + rollup | **SQLite** | 按 userId+agentId 索引查询 |\n\n路径建议（Studio / 本机）：\n\n```text\ndata/\n  users/<userId>/profile.save.json\n  memory/\n    memory.sqlite          # 或多文件 users/<userId>/memory.sqlite\n```\n\n壳侧可换路径；引擎只认 MemoryPort。\n\n## 2. 表结构初稿\n\n```sql\n-- 明细（episodic / semantic 等可用 layer 区分，或分表；v1 可用一张 entries）\nCREATE TABLE memory_entries (\n  id            TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id       TEXT NOT NULL,\n  agent_id      TEXT NOT NULL,\n  layer         TEXT NOT NULL,  -- episodic | semantic | commitment | …\n  kind          TEXT,           -- call_summary | vignette | beat | …\n  text          TEXT NOT NULL,\n  at            TEXT NOT NULL,  -- 事件/通话时刻 ISO\n  created_at    TEXT NOT NULL,\n  updated_at    TEXT NOT NULL,\n  call_id       TEXT,\n  importance    REAL,\n  fact_id       TEXT,\n  expires_at    TEXT,           -- affect 等\n  status        TEXT,           -- commitment\n  payload_json  TEXT            -- 其余层字段\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX idx_mem_user_agent_at","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":221,"fileSize":8444,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-969cfc14-4ffe-4f6c-a35c-a2469c0c9887-17\nfc_b5d6edd3-d965-94f8-86ea-b159bf8924eb_2","startedAtMs":"1784786274116","completedAtMs":"1784786274261"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-4-jbx6","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786274199}
