{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-27\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":300,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"```ts\n/** 纯 Free 会话的 packageId 哨兵；禁止对应 data/storis-packages/__free__/ */\nexport const FREE_PACKAGE_ID = \"__free__\"\n\ntype FreeCallPostPipeline = (ctx: {\n  session: CallSession\n  profile: PlayerProfile\n  transcript: unknown\n}) => Promise<void>\n```\n\n**v1 默认步骤（定稿）：**\n\n```text\n1. 有效聊天门闩（实质轮次 ≥ N；N 默认 2，可配置）\n2. 有效 → MemoryCommit（契约见 [12](../需求/12-记忆模型.md)：至少 call_summary + 可选 vignette；**条目必带时间戳**；文本 LLM 仅 server；可配置关闭）\n3. 若 session.exitCandidates 非空\n     → 与 Story 相同规则跑 ExitSelector\n       （静态 exits 可为空；纯动态须自带 effects）\n     → EffectExecutor + EffectSink + ledger\n   若为空 → 跳过 Exit（纯闲聊只记记忆）\n4. 写 jsonl + save Profile\n```\n\n**禁止：**\n\n- 从 transcript 隐式扫描「约定 / 介绍 / 回拨」再写 Profile\n- 对 `FREE_PACKAGE_ID` 调用 `loadPackage` / 创建故事目录\n\n**工具：** Free 默认全开 Registry 中 `free` 可用工具（旧话机业务 FC 抽来的七支，见 [13 §7](../需求/13-工具与能力注册.md)）；通话中仍只登记 candidate。\n\n注入：`createEngine({ freeCallPostPipeline })`。Story 卡仍走 Outcome → ExitSelector。\n\n---\n\n## 6. EffectExecutor vs EffectSink\n\n| 组件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| **EffectExecutor** | 引擎内：改 Profile（挂卡、fact、memory、variable、schedule 队列…）+ WET |\n| **EffectSink** | 壳/Studio：媒介副作用（留言、播 WAV、真响铃）；Studio 无硬件时为 mock |\n\n时序：\n\n```text\nExit 选中（或 Free pipeline 发出等价 effect）\n  → Executor 逐条：\n       · 逻辑类：改 Profile + WET\n       · 媒介类：先 WET（intent）→ 调用 EffectSink\n  → plan / pipeline 终态 → completed → save Profile","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":528,"fileSize":21926,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":300,"endLine":349},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-27\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_0","startedAtMs":"1784786295975","completedAtMs":"1784786296168"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-6-exmr","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786296116}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-28\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":460,"limit":70},"result":{"success":{"content":"---\n\n## 13. Outcome UX（调试器）\n\n- 默认 **Manual**（勾 beats / flags）。\n- 高级折叠：「文本模型建议 Outcome」→ 填入表单可改 → 用户确认后才 `endCall`。\n- v1 可不实现自动评估，保留入口位置。\n\n---\n\n## 14. 日志\n\n| 通道 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| Host 内存 ring | 调试时间线／WET 查询热源 |\n| `data/logs/engine-YYYYMMDD.jsonl` | 事件 + error；**旁路**，不整份塞进 SaveGame |\n| 可选「导出调试包」 | profile + 最近 session 快照 + log 切片 |\n\n**WET 与 Profile：** 逻辑事件只走 ring + jsonl；**禁止**把整份 WET 写入薄 Profile／SaveGame。幂等权威在通话内 `CallSession.effectLedger`。Studio 受控追加仅 `wet.annotation`／`wet.compensation`（标注／补偿说明），**只追加不改写**既有行，禁止借追加篡改 effect 历史。\n\n排障依赖 jsonl + 调试时间线；无 log 视为验收失败。\n\n---\n\n## 15. 错误码与 HTTP 映射\n\n响应体：`{ ok: boolean, code: string, message: string, details?: unknown }`\n\n| code | HTTP | 含义 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `OK` | 200 | |\n| `VALIDATION_FAILED` | 400 | Zod / 包校验 |\n| `UNAUTHORIZED` | 401 | 预留；v1 无密码几乎不用 |\n| `USER_REQUIRED` | 403 | 未选用户触及门禁后 API |\n| `NOT_FOUND` | 404 | user / package / card |\n| `CONFLICT_ACTIVE_CALL` | 409 | 已有活跃 Session |\n| `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE` | 409 | 不可拨打（未 effectiveDialable） |\n| `INVALID_PACKAGE_ID` | 400 | 对 `__free__` 哨兵误调 loadPackage 等 |\n| `STORY_LOCKED` | 409 | hard lock 拒绝 |\n| `NO_EXIT_MATCHED` | 422 | 仅 story 卡 |\n| `SCHEMA_UNSUPPORTED` | 422 | 版本过新/过旧且不可迁移 |\n| `ENGINE_INTERNAL` | 500 | |\n\n---\n\n## 16. 包版本 × Studio 拒载\n\n- `workspace` / package / SaveGame 均带整数 `schemaVersion`\n- 引擎 `SUPPORTED_SCHEMA = 1`（当前）\n- `file > SUPPORTED` → **拒载**；文案：「此内容由更新版引擎编写，请升级 Studio」\n- `file < SUPPORTED` 且无 migration → 拒载或只读（见 [17](./17-版本迁移与兼容策略.md)）；v1 仅版本 1 时非 1 一律 reject\n- UI：列表项禁用 + Dialog 说明；**禁止**静默损坏数据\n\n---\n\n## 17. 验收摘录\n\n- [x] Host 单例；同 user 通话互斥\n- [x] CallSession schema 可序列化调试快照；Free 用 `packageId=__free__`\n- [x] beginCall 带 composeScene（本地时间）；RenderedPrompt / matchedLayerIds 可观测\n- [x] 工作区为 `data/storis-packages/`；`story.conf.json` + `cards/*.s-card.json`；layout 旁车不进运行\n- [x] 单卡按需载入；禁止编辑真源依赖「全卡内联单文件」\n- [x] Free 卡路径：`data/characters/free-cards/`；禁止 load `__free__` 包目录\n- [x] UserGate 可在故事入口与调试器复用\n- [x] Free → PostPipeline（MemoryCommit；有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描\n- [x] `effectiveDialable` + `set_character_unlocked`\n- [ ] Sink 媒介时序正确；ledger + jsonl log\n- [x] 错误码表与 SCHEMA 拒载文案\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":528,"fileSize":21926,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":460,"endLine":528},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-28\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_1","startedAtMs":"1784786295979","completedAtMs":"1784786296184"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-6-exmr","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786296125}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-29\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md","offset":60,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"  + logs（jsonl）\n        ↑ Persistence / MemoryPort\n rpg-engine / EngineHost\n        ↑（仅快照 DTO）\n Studio Zustand（非真源）\n```\n\n**Content JSON ≠ Memory DB。** 存得下 ≠ 查得起、注得起。\n\n## 4. 端口落点\n\n| Port | 定义 | 实现位置 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| DialogueAdapter | 引擎接口 | Manual/Text → **Next server**；Realtime → 壳 |\n| OutcomeEvaluator | 引擎 Manual | Text 建议可放 server |\n| MemoryPort / LoreBootstrap | 引擎 | Memory：**SqliteMemoryPort**；LLM Commit 在 server |\n| PersistencePort | 引擎接口 | Studio：Content/薄 Profile 用 `fs`；Memory 用 sqlite |\n| EffectSink | 媒介 | Studio mock / 壳真执行 |\n| FreeCallPostPipeline | 引擎可注入 | 默认实现见 [19](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) |\n\n## 5. 其它\n\n- UI 简体中文；稳定 id 英文\n- 单包舒适 ≤ 80 卡节点\n- 条件为结构化谓词，禁止 `eval`\n- 本地单机 = `localhost` B/S\n- **不做**旧话机代码 / 配置 / 数据迁移；旧仓仅能力对标；新壳另建并嵌入本引擎\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":87,"fileSize":4559,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md","readRange":{"startLine":60,"endLine":87},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-29\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_2","startedAtMs":"1784786296159","completedAtMs":"1784786296299"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-6-exmr","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786296242}
