ack / Port）；现网 JSON+fs+SQLite 实现迁出到 Studio V2 `engineIOModule`。  \\n> **协议真源（工程）：** [技术设计 23-引擎存取Port与IO适配](../../技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。  \\n> **用法入口：** [packages/rpg-engine/README.md](../../../../packages/rpg-engine/README.md)。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. 本轮定位\\n\\n### 1.1 要做什么\\n\\n```text\\n程序边界\\n  · 引擎纯逻辑：不直接依赖 node:fs / better-sqlite3 实现\\n  · 引擎暴露存/取 Port（callback）+ 固定请求/响应协议\\n  · 宿主注入 Port；引擎只调 Port，不关心介质\\n\\n物理边界\\n  · 现网 IO 实现从 packages/rpg-engine 迁出\\n  · 落入 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/（本机 Studio 默认适配）\\n  · Next / Host 装配处创建并注入\\n\\n文档\\n  · 技术设计 23 为协议定稿；18/19/20 过期表述回写\\n  · 引擎 R [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-62eb9cf7-70aa-42ff-90c3-46a5cf76f417-7\\nfc_406b1aed-c85d-99d3-b24f-47e595ab3aa4_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"updateTodosToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"content\":\"对照 23 与现网，扫描 18/19/20/AGENTS/engine-boundaries/README 过期句\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_IN_PROGRESS\",\"createdAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"2\",\"content\":\"回写文档与规则交叉链接，使其与 Port/engineIOModule 一致\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_PENDING\",\"createdAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"content\":\"跑 quality:engine + quality:studio，通过后把 V2-IO-11 标 ✅\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_PENDING\",\"createdAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784786259912\",\"dependencies\":[]}],\"merge\":false}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-62eb9cf7-70aa-42ff-90c3-46a5cf76f417-7\\nfc_406b1aed-c85d-99d3-b24f-47e595ab3aa4_3\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784786259912\"},\"model_call_id\":\"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-2-9jmm\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-464 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-62eb9