ule`；Memory = SQLite  \n\n## 常用命令\n\n```bash\nnpm install                 # 根目录 workspace\nnpm run dev                 # Studio → http://localhost:3000\nnpm test                    # 引擎 Vitest + import 门禁（含 P1 Manual 闭环）\nnpm run check:engine-imports\nnpm run typecheck\nnpm run build\n```\n","message":"The file /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/AGENTS.md has been updated."}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-54226bf7-be82-4f3e-b160-41c1cbe18930-49\nfc_3b0d8035-5ea3-9b73-9630-94fac819e24d_4","startedAtMs":"1784786440758","completedAtMs":"1784786441148"},"model_call_id":"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-9-evby","session_id":"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc","timestamp_ms":1784786441092}
